OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers in
OL,6,FLothian and the Borders largely dying
OL,7,Fout with some clear intervals
OL,8,Fincreasing later. A few showers will
OL,9,Fcontinue across Dumfries and Galloway
OL,10,Fovernight.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FA mostly cloudy day. Mainly
OL,13,Fdry morning with just a few light
OL,14,Fshowers, then some more persistent
OL,15,Frain followed by heavy showers later.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,18,FRather cloudy with some showers on
OL,19,FThursday and early Friday. Brighter
OL,20,Fthereafter with sunny intervals and
OL,21,Fmore scattered showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
